WEBVTT

00:10:28.320 --> 00:10:30.548
a hkrati je zrasla tudi stopnja donosa

00:10:30.548 --> 00:10:32.760
na kapital

00:10:32.760 --> 00:10:34.690
in razlika med njima

00:10:34.690 --> 00:10:36.025
se ni spremenila.

00:10:36.025 --> 00:10:38.140
V 20. stoletju

00:10:38.140 --> 00:10:40.416
smo imeli edinstven sklop dogodkov.

00:10:40.416 --> 00:10:42.646
Prvič, zelo nizko stopnjo donosa

00:10:42.646 --> 00:10:45.570
zaradi šokov vojn leta 1914 in 1945,

00:10:45.570 --> 00:10:48.227
uničenja premoženja, inflacije,

00:10:48.227 --> 00:10:50.263
bankrota med veliko depresijo,

00:10:50.263 --> 00:10:51.598
vse to je spustilo

00:10:51.598 --> 00:10:54.278
zasebno stopnjo donosa na premoženje

00:10:54.278 --> 00:10:55.633
na nenavadno nizko raven

00:10:55.633 --> 00:10:58.303
med letoma 1914 in 1945.

00:10:58.303 --> 00:10:59.738
V povojnem obdobju

00:10:59.738 --> 00:11:02.097
je bila stopnja rasti nenavadno visoka,